reviewText: I like the old cartoons .  So I am happy with it.

The only cartoons on the whole DVD are Hector's Hectic Life, The Shanty Where Santy Claus Lives, and Christmas Night. Everything else is either a puppet show (the second video) or live-action. Slightly annoying, but considering I only paid $0.28 (minus shipping charges) I can't be too angry.
